  <brief_title>ECG Versus Ultrasound-guided Positioning of the Peripherally Inserted Central Catheter (PICC) Tip</brief_title>
  <official_title>ECG Versus Ultrasound-guided Positioning of the Peripherally Inserted Central Catheter (PICC) Tip</official_title>
